  "body": "<p>Paige worked a gorgeous event for a special guy on Saturday night. It's almost as though I was there the entire evening, though all I did was show up with some supplies and help set up. She stayed for the whole event working her magic. All these photos courtesy of <a href=\"http://www.paigeandchris.com/2012/06/one-with-ferrari-bar-mitzvah.html\">Paige's post</a>. Love that she remembers to take photos and that she shares them.</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"3a-DSC_4526.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766812636-4SOUDMF8MUTPCUA5MCSZ/3a-DSC_4526.jpg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"3b-DSC_4529.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766812660-AT21NF9FTHWHQWZX8I4P/3b-DSC_4529.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3c-DSC_4545.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766813510-FNPAM78PNU93JZNQPGDR/3c-DSC_4545.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3d-DSC_4539.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766813397-23EYJ37HXRXB1VWGVYVV/3d-DSC_4539.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3e-DSC_4533.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766814109-BWLSO2LW3WU3AAWWZ5CG/3e-DSC_4533.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3f-DSC_4534.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766814320-BBH26KIMQ5OCLB83TB18/3f-DSC_4534.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3g-DSC_4543.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766814957-DD66TIGSW0LRL9JSDEOY/3g-DSC_4543.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"3h-IMG_20120602_195918.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1600766815086-BF51NRSP004G5RMUILXQ/3h-IMG_20120602_195918.jpg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>We've worked many events with <a href=\"http://etchu.com/\">The Etch-A-Sketch Man</a> before (<a href=\"http://www.paigeandchris.com/2011/05/one-with-bar-mitzvah.html\">like this Bar Mitzvah last year</a>), and man watching him do his magic never gets old. The clients loved their scrapbook. And we certainly love our clients!</p>"
